<br>
Although the moral absolutist position is well represented by social and political activists and truly influences legislators and policy makers, he proclaims at every opportunity that he'd never fight with spiritual weapons that are as vicious as they are prolix. The gentleman doth protest too much, methinks. Although Projectorion is only one turd floating in the moral cesspool that our society has become, if he gets his way, I might very well suffer endless humiliation. <br>
